rComments: Definitely a very great educator. He can be sort of tough at the beginning, but as soon as you show your effort in the class he will try his best to help you with what you need.

awesome prof! lectures and creative assignments helped me understand the book better. I've learned a lot from this class, the assignments are based mainly on the lectures and some on the assigned readings. Pay attention to lectures, it will help you write the assignments.

This class is easy if you are a really good essay writer. He's a nice guy overall and I feel bad for saying this but I found that the lectures were really boring. You should read the textbook, the essays are heavily based on the textbook. I ended up getting an A even with my mediocre essay writing skills so it's a good class :)

I really love this guy. I love how he teaches and he connects so well with the students. I don't really care that I did sort of bad in this course, (I am a horrible essay writer) but this prof is really awesome!! I love going to this class :) Plus his smile is beautiful. I wish I can see him again :(
